    "page_content": "\"RAG\" usually refers to Retrieval-Augmented Generation, a technique in artificial intelligence that combines two powerful approaches:\n\n    🔍 Retrieval: The system searches a large database or knowledge source (like documents, articles, or the web) to find relevant information.\n\n    ✍️ Generation: A language model then uses that retrieved information to produce a coherent, context-aware answer.\n\nThis method is especially useful because:\n\n    It helps AI provide factual, up-to-date responses inste",
